#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:0
msgid "Continuous Integration with GitHub Actions and Cachix"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:0
msgid "NixOS, deployment, Terraform, AWS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:9
msgid "Deploying NixOS using Terraform"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:11
msgid ""
"Assuming you're [familiar with the basics of Terraform](https://www."
"terraform.io/intro/index.html), by the end of this tutorial you will have "
"provisioned an Amazon Web Services (AWS) instance with Terraform, and will "
"be able to use Nix to deploy incremental changes to NixOS running on the "
"instance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:13
msgid ""
"We'll look at how to boot a NixOS machine and how to deploy the incremental "
"changes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:15
msgid "Booting NixOS image"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:17
msgid "Start by providing the Terraform executable:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:19
msgid "$ nix-shell -p terraform\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:23
msgid ""
"We are using [Terraform Cloud](https://app.terraform.io) as a [state/locking "
"backend](https://www.terraform.io/docs/state/purpose.html):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:25
msgid "$ terraform login\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:29
msgid ""
"Make sure to [create an organization](https://app.terraform.io/app/"
"organizations/new), like `myorganization`, in your Terraform Cloud account."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:30
msgid ""
"Inside `myorganization`, [create a workspace](https://app.terraform.io/app/"
"cachix/workspaces/new) by choosing **CLI-driven workflow** and pick a name, "
"like  `myapp`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:31
msgid ""
"Inside your workspace, under `Settings / General`, change Execution Mode to "
"`Local`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:32
msgid ""
"Inside a new directory, create a `main.tf` file with the following contents. "
"This will start an AWS instance with the NixOS image using one SSH keypair "
"and an SSH security group:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:34
msgid ""
"terraform {\n"
"    backend \"remote\" {\n"
"        organization = \"myorganization\"\n"
"\n"
"        workspaces {\n"
"            name = \"myapp\"\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"provider \"aws\" {\n"
"    region = \"eu-central-1\"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"module \"nixos_image\" {\n"
"    source  = \"git::https://github.com/tweag/terraform-nixos.git//"
"aws_image_nixos?ref=5f5a0408b299874d6a29d1271e9bffeee4c9ca71\"\n"
"    release = \"20.09\"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"resource \"aws_security_group\" \"ssh_and_egress\" {\n"
"    ingress {\n"
"        from_port   = 22\n"
"        to_port     = 22\n"
"        protocol    = \"tcp\"\n"
"        cidr_blocks = [ \"0.0.0.0/0\" ]\n"
"    }\n"
"\n"
"    egress {\n"
"        from_port       = 0\n"
"        to_port         = 0\n"
"        protocol        = \"-1\"\n"
"        cidr_blocks     = [\"0.0.0.0/0\"]\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"resource \"tls_private_key\" \"state_ssh_key\" {\n"
"    algorithm = \"RSA\"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"resource \"local_file\" \"machine_ssh_key\" {\n"
"    sensitive_content = tls_private_key.state_ssh_key.private_key_pem\n"
"    filename          = \"${path.module}/id_rsa.pem\"\n"
"    file_permission   = \"0600\"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"resource \"aws_key_pair\" \"generated_key\" {\n"
"    key_name   = \"generated-key-${sha256(tls_private_key.state_ssh_key."
"public_key_openssh)}\"\n"
"    public_key = tls_private_key.state_ssh_key.public_key_openssh\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"resource \"aws_instance\" \"machine\" {\n"
"    ami             = module.nixos_image.ami\n"
"    instance_type   = \"t3.micro\"\n"
"    security_groups = [ aws_security_group.ssh_and_egress.name ]\n"
"    key_name        = aws_key_pair.generated_key.key_name\n"
"\n"
"    root_block_device {\n"
"        volume_size = 50 # GiB\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"output \"public_dns\" {\n"
"    value = aws_instance.machine.public_dns\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:101
msgid "The only NixOS specific snippet is:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:103
msgid ""
"module \"nixos_image\" {\n"
"  source = \"git::https://github.com/tweag/terraform-nixos.git/"
"aws_image_nixos?ref=5f5a0408b299874d6a29d1271e9bffeee4c9ca71\"\n"
"  release = \"20.09\"\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:111
msgid ""
"The `aws_image_nixos` module will return a NixOS AMI given a [NixOS release "
"number](https://status.nixos.org) so that the `aws_instance` resource can "
"reference the AMI in the [instance_type](https://registry.terraform.io/"
"providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs/resources/instance#instance_type) "
"argument."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:115
msgid ""
"Make sure to [configure AWS credentials](https://registry.terraform.io/"
"providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs#authentication)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:116
msgid "Applying the Terraform configuration should get you a running NixOS:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:118
#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:151
msgid ""
"$ terraform init\n"
"$ terraform apply\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:123
msgid "Deploying NixOS changes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:125
msgid ""
"Once the AWS instance is running a NixOS image via Terraform, we can teach "
"Terraform to always build the latest NixOS configuration and apply those "
"changes to your instance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:127
msgid "Create `configuration.nix` with the following contents:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:129
msgid ""
"{ config, lib, pkgs, ... }: {\n"
"  imports = [ <nixpkgs/nixos/modules/virtualisation/amazon-image.nix> ];\n"
"\n"
"  # Open https://search.nixos.org/options for all options\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:137
msgid "Append the following snippet to your `main.tf`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:139
msgid ""
"module \"deploy_nixos\" {\n"
"    source = \"git::https://github.com/tweag/terraform-nixos.git//"
"deploy_nixos?ref=5f5a0408b299874d6a29d1271e9bffeee4c9ca71\"\n"
"    nixos_config = \"${path.module}/configuration.nix\"\n"
"    target_host = aws_instance.machine.public_ip\n"
"    ssh_private_key_file = local_file.machine_ssh_key.filename\n"
"    ssh_agent = false\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:149
msgid "Deploy:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:156
msgid "Caveats"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:158
msgid ""
"The `deploy_nixos` module requires NixOS to be installed on the target "
"machine and Nix on the host machine."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:159
msgid ""
"The `deploy_nixos` module doesn't work when the client and target "
"architectures are different (unless you use [distributed builds](https://nix."
"dev/manual/nix/stable/advanced-topics/distributed-builds.html))."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:160
msgid "If you need to inject a value into Nix, there is no elegant solution."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:161
msgid ""
"Each machine is evaluated separately, so note that your memory requirements "
"will grow linearly with the number of machines."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:163
msgid "Next steps"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:165
msgid ""
"It's possible to [switch to Google Compute Engine](https://github.com/tweag/"
"terraform-nixos/tree/master/google_image_nixos#readme)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/deploying-nixos-using-terraform.md:166
msgid ""
"The [`deploy_nixos` module](https://github.com/tweag/terraform-nixos/tree/"
"master/deploy_nixos#readme) supports a number of arguments, for example to "
"upload keys."
msgstr ""
